&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive compensation package&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;and unique benefits designed to support your growth and well-being.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;100% Remote Work from Europe / South America,&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;with access to global CoWorking spaces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work-Life Balance:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Up to 35 vacation days, 30 sick days and parental leave&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Learning:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Access to training programs, language courses, and learning sponsorship annually.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unique Projects:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Work with cutting-edge blockchain technology in a global, diverse team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monthly Allowance&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;for Contractors to support your connectivity and well-being.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
